[src:stochastic-calculus/girsanov-theorem] This was Igor Girsanov's original formulation of the above theorem.
[src:stochastic-calculus/girsanov-theorem] Another application of this theorem, also given in the original paper of Igor Girsanov, is for stochastic differential equations.
